writablefield_set_font
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Header:	<Gadgets.H=>gadgets>
Class:	<Writable Fields=>writables>
#Line
Syntax:	
#indent 6
{FCode}extern <_kernel_oserror> *writablefield_set_font 
(
  unsigned int  flags,
  <ObjectId>      window,
  <ComponentId>   writable,
  char         *font_name,
  int           width,
  int           height
);

{F}
#indent
Purpose:	Function makes the writable field specified in ComponentId use the anti-aliased font specified in {/}font_name{/}.  If the field is set to NULL, then the system font is used.